  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In the not-too-distant future, a terrible virus affects humanity, turning most of it into zombies. You, as one of the last survivals, will have to fight your way to the place where it all began and put an end to it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you adore the tower defense genre, but sometimes you lack dynamics, then you've come to the right place. Our team offers you a new take on this genre, where we tried to add more action, dynamics and non-linearity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>TOWER DEFENSE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A variety of buildings with different functionality will allow you to customize the game for yourself. In our game, we have given up premeditated and optimal places for building, any of your adventures can work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>WEAPONS AND CUSTOMIZATION</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>And don't forget to stand out by getting a unique character skin or weapon after successfully completing a level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>UNIQUE LOCATIONS AND BOSSES</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>7 completely different locations with unique enemies and bosses will definitely not let you get bored, and the hard mode will challenge you really hard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build, adapt and have as much fun as possible - this is the motto of our game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In the not-too-distant future, a terrible virus affects humanity, turning most of it into zombies. You, as one of the last survivals, will have to fight your way to the place where it all began and put an end to it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you adore the tower defense genre, but sometimes you lack dynamics, then you've come to the right place. Our team offers you a new take on this genre, where we tried to add more action, dynamics and non-linearity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>TOWER DEFENSE</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9bb4d7211afcd8ee4414f655b66ab16e.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>A variety of buildings with different functionality will allow you to customize the game for yourself. In our game, we have given up premeditated and optimal places for building, any of your adventures can work!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>WEAPONS AND CUSTOMIZATION</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/9808cd04319f7f41102cdcdd408b0f88.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>And don't forget to stand out by getting a unique character skin or weapon after successfully completing a level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>UNIQUE LOCATIONS AND BOSSES</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.poster.avif?t=1756023304\" width=624 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.webm?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011200/extras/5217b77129132dbdda696beb00c5af33.mp4?t=1756023304\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>7 completely different locations with unique enemies and bosses will definitely not let you get bored, and the hard mode will challenge you really hard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build, adapt and have as much fun as possible - this is the motto of our game.</p>",
